    <property>
      <answer>For individual patient records, there is an //Export XAR// option in the //More Actions// menu in the top right corner of the page, but **that entry is only shown for "advanced" users.**

If you do not see that option, then you must switch your user type from simple to advanced:

1. open your user profile by clicking on your name in the upper right corner
1. click the pencil icon on the right of //Personal Information//
1. open the //Preferences// tab from the list on the left
1. change the //User Type// option to ##Advanced##
1. save

The option //Export XAR// should now show up in the //More Actions// menu for all patient records.
</answer>
